data.description: Turn Key CBS Home with a new steel roof and AC system ready for you to enjoy the warm winters and sunny beaches. This property has been lovingly remodeled and landscaped like a tropical oasis with a fenced in back yard, Hot Tub, a shed and a garden. This gem is located in the heart of the desirable North Palm Beach community but Zoned as West Palm Beach Unincorporated gives you the best of both worlds. This zoning which is only on Richard Rd and Hinda allows you more freedom over the rules of NPB. You can park you Boat or RV in your yard!
